===Format===
* '''Group Stage:''''' January 6th - 9th, 2025
** 64 teams, 4 Matchdays.
*** {{bgcolortext|stayup|32 teams}} from Open Qualifiers.
*** {{bgcolortext|stayup|32 teams}} directly invited.
** Teams are divided equally into 4 groups of 16 Teams each.
** Each group will play 6 matches.
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 8 Teams}} from each group advance to ''Semi Finals''.
<div style="margin-top:1em"></div>
* '''Semi Finals:''''' January 13th - 16th, 2025
** 32 teams, 4 Matchdays.
** Teams are divided equally into 2 groups of 16 teams each.
** Each group play 12 matches.
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 8 Teams}} from each group qualify for ''Grand Finals''.
<div style="margin-top:1em"></div>
* '''Grand Finals:''''' January 20th - 26th, 2025
** 16 teams, 4 Matchdays.
** 24 matches (6 each day).
<br/>
